## Overview
Make Telenor data-, insight-, and AI-driven. This objective looks to exploit data to create more value to the organization, either by using analytical tools for insights, or AI tools for automation or assistance.
## Goals
* Understand how much value there is by exploiting data for analytical and automation
* Define an ambition level and a roadmap to get there
* Increase organizational knowledge on Data Mesh's principles (domain-oriented ownership, data as a product, federated computational governance, and self-serve data platform)
* Equip [[Shared Data Services Value Stream]] to start enabling the transformation on data for Telenor Norway
